Seed investor in some of the most exciting French & British startups including:
- SeedLegals.com is the SaaS platform where startups raise investment & digitize operations ;
- PlayPlay.com (French Tech 120) is simply the best tool for companies to produce and publish digital videos online ;
- Indy.fr blends together SaaS and IA to automate accounting services for sole traders ;
- Papier.com is the global leader in design-led, personalized stationery products made on-demand ;
- Asap TT disrupts the oligopoly of temp workers in the construction industry ;
- Nomalab.com operates the one and only "lab in a browser" to re-purpose video assets for global B2B distribution ;
- Belleviecare.co.uk is the most elegant and trusted solution for older people needing care at home in the UK ;
- Uni-Quest.co.uk [exited] operates a SaaS platform to help Universities enroll international students.
